{"tid":558244,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發冇圖 俾港鐵淫女引","createTime":"2018-02-12T06:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T17:49:25.000Z","uid":146869,"like":2,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b5b3ec4eb51fa016a15872305fbd19af60cda1ad","tid":558244,"uid":146869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:06:46.000Z","msg":"坐坐吓對面坐咗個短裙淫女 成對長腿伸哂出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲由坐底開始望住我 擺撚到明想我眼神強姦佢<br />\n身為毒撚對住個咁aggressive既淫閪邊敢欣賞佢對淫腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲周不時望手機同電視轉移視線<br />\n最後條女知道引唔到我呢個聖人就落咗車<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚正阿 如果唔係坐得太近實影底佢對淫腳俾一眾巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌得細力啲"},{"pid":"f2ba25832f48d92d8e8615013fb3516002fb83f7","tid":558244,"uid":55939,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:09:09.000Z","msg":"突然聽到 鈴、鈴、鈴<br />\n我彈起身 望見條褲濕左一達"},{"pid":"55d1e836518c6a1d3c83094f8f56da94df2297cf","tid":558244,"uid":136760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2ba25832f48d92d8e8615013fb3516002fb83f7","tid":558244,"uid":55939,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:09:09.000Z","msg":"突然聽到 鈴、鈴、鈴<br />\n我彈起身 望見條褲濕左一達"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f37f6fdb6b6fade688b5dd0db15844bce608f17","tid":558244,"uid":169468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:20:41.000Z","msg":"你太耐冇返屋企，嗰個係伯母嚟"},{"pid":"c6646a4cba30264650118f7937f3f74812ceae7f","tid":558244,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:30:56.000Z","msg":"少啲ff"},{"pid":"25f323fdbadfc576946e6ac402dc461116bea16e","tid":558244,"uid":131548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12